#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:255
msgid ""
"POS product categories are used to group products in the POS register to aid "
"navigation."
msgstr ""
"Kassaproductcategorieën worden gebruikt om producten in de kassa te "
"groeperen en zo de navigatie te vergemakkelijken."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:257
msgid "To manage POS categories, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Volg deze stappen om kassacategorieën te beheren:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:259
