msgid ""
"**Green** :icon:`fa-list` (:guilabel:`Valid product lot`) **icon**: The "
"tracking number was successfully imported or assigned."
msgstr ""
"**Groen** :icon:`fa-list` (:guilabel:`Geldig productlot`) **icoon**: Het "
"volgnummer is succesvol geïmporteerd of toegewezen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/products.rst:452
msgid ""
"**Red** :icon:`fa-list` (:guilabel:`Invalid product lot`) **icon**: The "
"tracking number is missing or incorrect."
msgstr ""
"**Rood** :icon:`fa-list` (:guilabel:`Ongeldig productlot`) **icoon**: Het "
"volgnummer ontbreekt of is onjuist."

