#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:128
msgid ""
"To use the UrbanPiper integration in a live production environment, ensure "
"the following requirements are satisfied:"
msgstr ""
"Om de UrbanPiper-integratie in een live productieomgeving te gebruiken, zorg "
"je ervoor dat aan de volgende vereisten is voldaan:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:131
msgid ""
"**UrbanPiper subscription:** A valid UrbanPiper subscription is mandatory."
msgstr ""
"**UrbanPiper-abonnement:** Een geldig UrbanPiper-abonnement is verplicht."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:134
msgid ""
"For any concerns or queries regarding your UrbanPiper subscription, please "
"reach out to the account manager linked to your Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"Neem voor eventuele zorgen of vragen over je UrbanPiper-abonnement contact "
"op met de accountmanager die aan je Odoo-database is gekoppeld."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:137
msgid "**Odoo requirements:**"
msgstr "**Odoo-vereisten:**"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:139
msgid ""
"**Odoo subscription:** An active Odoo Enterprise subscription is required. "
"Odoo Community does not support this integration."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo-abonnement:** Een actief Odoo Enterprise-abonnement is vereist. Odoo "
"Community ondersteunt deze integratie niet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:141
msgid "**Odoo version:** Odoo Enterprise version 18.0 or above."
msgstr "**Odoo-versie:** Odoo Enterprise versie 18.0 of hoger."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:142
msgid ""
"**Odoo platform:** All Odoo platforms are supported, including Odoo Online, "
"Odoo.sh, and On-Premise installations."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo-platform:** Alle Odoo-platforms worden ondersteund, inclusief Odoo "
"Online, Odoo.sh en On-Premise installaties."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:145
msgid ""
"**Delivery platform reseller account:** A registered reseller account is "
"required with each delivery platform to be integrated (e.g., Uber Eats, "
"DoorDash, Careem, Deliveroo, Zomato)."
msgstr ""
"**Reseller-rekening bezorgplatform:** Een geregistreerd reseller-account is "
"vereist voor elk bezorgplatform dat wordt geïntegreerd (bv. Uber Eats, "
"DoorDash, Careem, Deliveroo, Zomato)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:151
msgid "UrbanPiper credentials"
msgstr "UrbanPiper-inloggegevens"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:153
