msgstr ""
"Scroll naar beneden naar het gedeelte :guilabel:`Food Delivery Connector`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/restaurant/urban_piper.rst:157
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Fill this form to get Username & Api key` and fill out the "
"survey."
msgstr ""
"Klik op :guilabel:`Fill this form to get Username & Api key` en vul de "
"enquête in."

