msgstr "Klik op :guilabel:`Klant`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:148
msgid "Enter the customer's details, then click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr "Voer de gegevens van de klant in en klik op :guilabel:`Opslaan`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:150
msgid "To create customers from the backend:"
msgstr "Klanten aanmaken vanuit de backend:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:152
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Orders --> Customers`."
msgstr "Ga naar :menuselection:`Kassa --> Orders --> Klanten`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:153
msgid "Click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr "Klik op :guilabel:`Nieuw`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:154
msgid "Enter the customer's details and save."
msgstr "Voer de gegevens van de klant in en sla ze op."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:156
msgid ""
"To assign a customer to an order in the POS register or on the payment "
"screen, click :guilabel:`Customer` and select the desired customer. To "
"select a different customer, click the current customer's name on the "
"numpad, then select another one."
msgstr ""
"Klik op :guilabel:`Klant` om een klant aan een order toe te wijzen in het "
"kassaregister of op het betalingsscherm en selecteer de gewenste klant. Klik "
"op de naam van de huidige klant op het cijferpaneel om een andere klant te "
"selecteren en selecteer vervolgens een andere."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:161
msgid ""
"To edit the customer's details, click the customer's name on the numpad, "
"click the :icon:`fa-bars` (:guilabel:`hamburger menu`) icon next to the "
"relevant customer, then select :guilabel:`Edit Details`."
msgstr ""
"Klik op de naam van de klant op het cijferpaneel om de gegevens van de klant "
"te bewerken, klik op het :icon:`fa-bars` (:guilabel:`hamburgermenu`) icoon "
"naast de relevante klant en selecteer vervolgens :guilabel:`Bewerk details`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:166
msgid ""
"Creating a new customer in the POS register or on the payment screen "
"automatically assigns them to the current order upon saving."
msgstr ""
"Een nieuwe klant aanmaken in het kassaregister of op het betalingsscherm "
"wijst deze automatisch toe aan de huidige order bij het opslaan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:170
msgid "Send marketing messages"
msgstr "Marketingberichten versturen"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:172
msgid ""
"Customers' contact details, such as phone numbers or email addresses, are "
"automatically stored when :doc:`receipts <use/receipts>` are sent via email, "
"SMS, or WhatsApp. They can then be used, for example, for marketing purposes."
msgstr ""
"Contactgegevens van klanten, zoals telefoonnummers of e-mailadressen, worden "
"automatisch opgeslagen wanneer :doc:`kassatickets <use/receipts>` per e-"
"mail, sms of WhatsApp worden verzonden. Ze kunnen vervolgens bijvoorbeeld "
"voor marketingdoeleinden worden gebruikt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:176
msgid ""
"To send marketing messages manually from the POS backend, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Volg deze stappen om handmatig marketingberichten te verzenden vanuit de "
"kassa-backend:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:178
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use/pos_invoices.rst:88
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use/pos_invoices.rst:101
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use/pos_invoices.rst:124
msgid "Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Orders --> Orders`."
msgstr "Ga naar :menuselection:`Kassa --> Bestellingen --> Bestellingen`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:179
msgid "Click a POS order and open the :guilabel:`Extra Info` tab."
msgstr "Klik op een kassaorder en open het :guilabel:`Extra info`-tabblad."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:180
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Contact Info` category, click the :icon:`fa-envelope` "
"(:guilabel:`email`) icon or the :icon:`fa-whatsapp` (:guilabel:`WhatsApp`) "
"icon next to the completed :guilabel:`Email` or :guilabel:`Mobile` field."
msgstr ""
"Klik onder de categorie :guilabel:`Contactinfo` op het :icon:`fa-envelope` "
"(:guilabel:`e-mail`) icoon of het :icon:`fa-whatsapp` (:guilabel:`WhatsApp`) "
"icoon naast het ingevulde :guilabel:`E-mail`- of :guilabel:`Telefoon`-veld."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:185
msgid ""
"Make sure a customer is assigned to the order to send marketing messages "
"manually."
msgstr ""
"Zorg ervoor dat een klant aan de order is toegewezen om handmatig "
"marketingberichten te verzenden."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:188
msgid ":doc:`../../marketing/email_marketing`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../marketing/email_marketing`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:189
msgid ":doc:`../../marketing/sms_marketing`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../marketing/sms_marketing`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:190
msgid ":doc:`../../productivity/whatsapp`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../productivity/whatsapp`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:195
msgid "Access the orders overview"
msgstr "Open het ordersoverzicht"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:197
msgid ""
"The orders overview allows for viewing, searching, and retrieving orders "
"from the POS interface. To access it, click :guilabel:`Orders` in the POS "
"interface header."
msgstr ""
"Het ordersoverzicht maakt het mogelijk om orders te bekijken, te zoeken en "
"op te halen vanuit de kassainterface. Klik op :guilabel:`Orders` in de "
"header van de kassainterface om het te openen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:200
msgid ""
"To filter orders based on their status, click the :guilabel:`Active` "
"dropdown menu and select one of the following options:"
msgstr ""
"Filter orders op basis van hun status door op het dropdown-"
"menu :guilabel:`Actief` te klikken en een van de volgende opties te "
"selecteren:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:203
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Active`: Orders currently in progress. This includes orders "
"marked as :guilabel:`Ongoing`, as well as those in the :guilabel:`Payment` "
"or the :guilabel:`Receipt` stages (i.e., orders for which the receipt has "
"been emailed to the customer)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Actief`: Orders die momenteel bezig zijn. Dit omvat orders "
"gemarkeerd als :guilabel:`Lopend`, evenals orders in de "
"fases :guilabel:`Betaling` of :guilabel:`Ontvangstbewijs` (d.w.z. orders "
"waarvoor het ontvangstbewijs per e-mail naar de klant is verzonden)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:206
msgid ":guilabel:`Paid`: Paid orders."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Betaald`: Betaalde orders."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:207
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Cancelled`: Orders cancelled on online platforms "
"through :ref:`UrbanPiper <pos/urban_piper/configuration>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Geannuleerd`: Bestellingen geannuleerd op online platforms "
"via :ref:`UrbanPiper <pos/urban_piper/configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:210
msgid ""
"It is also possible to search for orders based on, for example, "
"the :guilabel:`Receipt Number`, :guilabel:`Date`, or :guilabel:`Customer`."
msgstr ""
"Het is ook mogelijk om orders te zoeken op basis van bijvoorbeeld "
"het :guilabel:`Bonummer`, :guilabel:`Datum` of :guilabel:`Klant`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:213
msgid ""
"To navigate between pages, click the :icon:`fa-caret-left` or :icon:`fa-"
"caret-right` (:guilabel:`caret`) icon."
msgstr ""
"Navigeer tussen pagina's door op het :icon:`fa-caret-left` of :icon:`fa-"
"caret-right` (:guilabel:`caret`) icoon te klikken."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:216
msgid ""
"To access an order in the register, click it, then click :guilabel:`Load "
"Order`."
msgstr ""
"Open een order in de kassa door erop te klikken en vervolgens "
"op :guilabel:`Order Laden` te klikken."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:219
msgid ":guilabel:`Paid` orders can be :ref:`refunded <pos/use/refund>`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Betaalde` orders kunnen worden :ref:`terugbetaald <pos/use/"
"refund>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:222
msgid ""
"To define the number of orders visible on a page, click `1-x / x`. Enter a "
"number lower than the total number of pages, and click :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Voer een getal in dat lager is dan het totale aantal pagina's en klik "
"op :guilabel:`Bevestigen` om het aantal orders te definiëren dat op een "
"pagina zichtbaar is."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:224
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-trash` (:guilabel:`trash`) icon next to "
"an :guilabel:`Active` order to delete it."
msgstr ""
"Klik op het :icon:`fa-trash` (:guilabel:`prullenbak`) icoon naast "
"een :guilabel:`Actieve` order om deze te verwijderen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:226
msgid ""
"If using :doc:`presets <extra/presets>`, click one to view the related "
"orders. Click it again to return to the main overview."
msgstr ""
"Als je :doc:`presets <extra/presets>` gebruikt, klik je op een preset om de "
"gerelateerde bestellingen te bekijken. Klik er opnieuw op om terug te keren "
"naar het hoofdoverzicht."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:232
msgid "Return and refund products"
msgstr "Producten inleveren en terugbetalen"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:234
msgid ""
"The steps to process a refund from the :ref:`POS register <pos/use/open-"
"register>` depend on whether the refund is :ref:`based on an order <pos/use/"
"refund-order-based>` or processed as a :ref:`standalone refund that is not "
"based on an order <pos/use/refund-standalone>`."
msgstr ""
"De stappen om een terugbetaling te verwerken vanaf de :ref:`kassa <pos/use/"
"open-register>` hangen af van of de terugbetaling :ref:`gebaseerd is op een "
"order <pos/use/refund-order-based>` of wordt verwerkt als "
"een :ref:`zelfstandige terugbetaling die niet is gebaseerd op een order <pos/"
"use/refund-standalone>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:238
msgid ""
"In both cases, the amount can be refunded or a :ref:`gift card <pos/pricing/"
"loyalty>` issued for the refunded amount."
msgstr ""
"In beide gevallen kan het bedrag worden terugbetaald of kan er "
"een :ref:`cadeaubon <pos/pricing/loyalty>` worden uitgegeven voor het "
"terugbetaalde bedrag."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:242
msgid ""
"Once the return is validated, a corresponding credit note is generated, "
"referencing the original :doc:`receipt <use/receipts>` or :doc:`invoice <use/"
"pos_invoices>`."
msgstr ""
"Zodra de inlevering is gevalideerd, wordt een bijbehorende creditfactuur "
"gegenereerd die verwijst naar het oorspronkelijke :doc:`ontvangstbewijs <use/"
"receipts>` of de oorspronkelijke :doc:`factuur <use/pos_invoices>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:246
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/credit_notes`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:251
msgid "Order-based refunds"
msgstr "Terugbetalingen op basis van orders"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:253
msgid "To process a refund based on an order, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Volg deze stappen om een terugbetaling op basis van een order te verwerken:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:255
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`vertical ellipsis`) icon in the "
"POS register."
msgstr ""
"Klik op het :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`verticale beletseltekens`) "
"icoon in de kassa."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:256
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Refund`. The orders overview opens, displaying "
"all :guilabel:`Paid` orders."
msgstr ""
"Selecteer :guilabel:`Terugbetaling`. Het ordersoverzicht wordt geopend en "
"toont alle :guilabel:`Betaalde` orders."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:257
msgid ""
"Select the product(s) to refund, and then enter the quantity to refund if "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"Selecteer de product(en) om terug te betalen en voer indien nodig de "
"hoeveelheid in die je wilt terugbetalen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:258
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Refund` to open the payment screen."
msgstr "Klik op :guilabel:`Terugbetaling` om het betalingsscherm te openen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:259
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:287
msgid "Choose how to handle the refund:"
msgstr "Kies hoe je de terugbetaling wilt afhandelen:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:261
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:289
msgid ""
"To refund the customer, on the payment screen, select a payment method, then "
"click :guilabel:`Validate`."
msgstr ""
"Selecteer op het betalingsscherm een betaalmethode en klik vervolgens "
"op :guilabel:`Valideren` om de klant terug te betalen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:263
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:291
msgid ""
"To issue a :ref:`gift card <pos/pricing/loyalty>` for the refund amount, on "
"the payment screen, click :guilabel:`Back`. The cart displays the returned "
"product(s) with a negative quantity. Then, add the gift card from the "
"product selector to the order; its value is automatically set to match the "
"total refund amount. Click :guilabel:`Payment`, then :guilabel:`Validate` "
"the refund."
msgstr ""
"Klik op het betalingsscherm op :guilabel:`Terug` om een :ref:`cadeaubon <pos/"
"pricing/loyalty>` uit te geven voor het terugbetalingsbedrag. Het "
"winkelmandje toont het/de ingeleverde product(en) met een negatieve "
"hoeveelheid. Voeg vervolgens de cadeaubon toe vanuit de productkiezer aan de "
"order; de waarde wordt automatisch ingesteld om overeen te komen met het "
"totale terugbetalingsbedrag. Klik op :guilabel:`Betaling` "
"en :guilabel:`Valideer` vervolgens de terugbetaling."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:270
msgid ""
"Alternatively, access the list of paid orders by clicking :guilabel:`Orders` "
"in the POS interface header and selecting :guilabel:`Paid` from "
"the :guilabel:`Active` dropdown menu."
msgstr ""
"Je kunt ook toegang krijgen tot de lijst met betaalde orders door "
"op :guilabel:`Orders` te klikken in de header van de kassainterface "
"en :guilabel:`Betaald` te selecteren in het :guilabel:`Actief` dropdownmenu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:272
msgid ""
"Refunds can also be initiated and processed from the backend. To do so, go "
"to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Orders --> Orders`, select an order, "
"then click :guilabel:`Return Products`. Note that this method can only be "
"used to refund the entire order."
msgstr ""
"Terugbetalingen kunnen ook worden geïnitieerd en verwerkt vanuit de backend. "
"Ga hiervoor naar :menuselection:`Kassa --> Orders --> Orders`, selecteer een "
"order en klik vervolgens op :guilabel:`Producten inleveren`. Merk op dat "
"deze methode alleen kan worden gebruikt om de volledige order terug te "
"betalen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:279
msgid "Standalone refunds"
msgstr "Zelfstandige terugbetalingen"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:281
msgid ""
"To process a standalone refund that is *not* based on an order, follow these "
"steps:"
msgstr ""
"Volg deze stappen om een zelfstandige terugbetaling te verwerken die *niet* "
"is gebaseerd op een order:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:283
msgid "Select the relevant product from the POS register."
msgstr "Selecteer het relevante product via de kassa."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:284
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Qty` to enter the quantity to refund, then "
"click :guilabel:`+/-` to set it as a negative quantity."
msgstr ""
"Klik op :guilabel:`Hoeveelheid` om de terug te betalen hoeveelheid in te "
"voeren en klik vervolgens op :guilabel:`+/-` om deze als negatieve "
"hoeveelheid in te stellen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:286
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Payment` to open the payment screen."
msgstr "Klik op :guilabel:`Betaling` om het betalingsscherm te openen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:298
msgid ""
"To facilitate management of standalone returns, create a :doc:`preset <extra/"
"presets>` with only the :guilabel:`Return mode` enabled. When this preset is "
"selected from the POS register, the quantity of any item added to the cart "
"is set to negative."
msgstr ""
"Om het beheer van zelfstandige inleveringen te vereenvoudigen, maak je "
"een :doc:`voorinstelling <extra/presets>` aan met alleen "
"de :guilabel:`Inlevermodus` ingeschakeld. Wanneer deze voorinstelling is "
"geselecteerd via de kassa, wordt de hoeveelheid van elk artikel dat aan het "
"winkelmandje wordt toegevoegd, op negatief gezet."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:305
msgid "Add and manage notes"
msgstr "Notities toevoegen en beheren"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:307
msgid ""
"Notes allow for extra information to be added to specific products in an "
"order. There are two types of notes: :ref:`internal notes <pos/use/internal-"
"notes>` and :ref:`customer notes <pos/use/customer-notes>`."
msgstr ""
"Met notities kun je extra informatie toevoegen aan specifieke producten in "
"een bestelling. Er zijn twee soorten notities: :ref:`interne notities <pos/"
"use/internal-notes>` en :ref:`klantnotities <pos/use/customer-notes>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:312
msgid ""
"If the same content is frequently used, configure a note model to save time. "
"To create or edit note models, go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> "
"Configuration --> Note Models`, click :guilabel:`New` or click the relevant "
"note model, then complete or edit the :guilabel:`Name` column."
msgstr ""
"Als dezelfde inhoud vaak wordt gebruikt, configureer je een notitiemodel om "
"tijd te besparen. Om notitiemodellen aan te maken of te bewerken, ga je "
"naar :menuselection:`Kassa --> Configuratie --> Notitiemodellen`, klik je "
"op :guilabel:`Nieuw` of klik je op het relevante notitiemodel en vul je "
"vervolgens de kolom :guilabel:`Naam` in of bewerk je deze."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:318
msgid ""
"Any customer notes added to a product from the :ref:`POS register <pos/use/"
"open-register>` are displayed on the :doc:`customer display <../"
"point_of_sale/hardware_network/customer_display>`."
msgstr ""
"Alle klantnotities die via de :ref:`kassa <pos/use/open-register>` aan een "
"product worden toegevoegd, worden weergegeven op het :doc:`klantscherm <../"
"point_of_sale/hardware_network/customer_display>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:324
msgid "Internal notes"
msgstr "Interne notities"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:326
msgid ""
"Internal notes provide information intended for staff (e.g., `no tomato` for "
"the kitchen team) and do not appear on the customer's receipt."
msgstr ""
"Interne notities bieden informatie die bedoeld is voor personeel (bv. `geen "
"tomaat` voor het keukenpersoneel) en verschijnen niet op het ontvangstbewijs "
"van de klant."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:329
msgid ""
"To add or edit an internal note from the POS register, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Volg deze stappen om een interne notitie toe te voegen of te bewerken via de "
"kassa:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:331
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:349
msgid "If the note applies to:"
msgstr "Als de notitie van toepassing is op:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:333
msgid ""
"The entire order: Ensure no item is selected in the cart, then "
"click :guilabel:`Note`."
msgstr ""
"De hele bestelling: zorg dat er geen artikel is geselecteerd in het "
"winkelmandje en klik vervolgens op :guilabel:`Notitie`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:334
msgid ""
"A specific item: Select the item in the cart, then click :guilabel:`Note`."
msgstr ""
"Een specifiek artikel: selecteer het artikel in het winkelmandje en klik "
"vervolgens op :guilabel:`Notitie`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:335
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:355
msgid ""
"Add or modify the note's content in the popover or select a previously "
"configured note model."
msgstr ""
"Voeg de inhoud van de notitie toe of wijzig deze in de popover of selecteer "
"een eerder geconfigureerd notitiemodel."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:336
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:356
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Apply`."
msgstr "Klik op :guilabel:`Toepassen`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:341
msgid "Customer notes"
msgstr "Klantnotities"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:343
msgid ""
"Customer notes appear on :doc:`receipts <use/receipts>` and :doc:`invoices "
"<use/pos_invoices>`. They can be used, for example, to provide warranty "
"details for a high-value item or specific care instructions, such as `Dry "
"clean only`."
msgstr ""
"Klantnotities verschijnen op :doc:`ontvangstbewijzen <use/receipts>` "
"en :doc:`verkoopfacturen <use/pos_invoices>`. Ze kunnen bijvoorbeeld worden "
"gebruikt om garantiegegevens voor een waardevol artikel te verstrekken of "
"specifieke verzorgingsinstructies, zoals `Alleen stomen`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:347
msgid ""
"To add or edit a customer note from the POS register, follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Volg deze stappen om een klantnotitie toe te voegen of te bewerken via de "
"kassa:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:351
msgid ""
"The entire order: Ensure no item is selected in the cart, click "
"the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`vertical ellipsis`) icon, then "
"click :guilabel:`Customer Note`."
msgstr ""
"De hele bestelling: zorg dat er geen artikel is geselecteerd in het "
"winkelmandje, klik op het icoon :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`verticale "
"ellips`) en klik vervolgens op :guilabel:`Klantnotitie`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/use.rst:353
msgid ""
"A specific item: Select the item in the cart, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-"
"v` (:guilabel:`vertical ellipsis`) icon, then click :guilabel:`Customer "
"Note`."
msgstr ""
"Een specifiek artikel: selecteer het artikel in het winkelmandje, klik op "
"het icoon :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`verticale ellips`) en klik "
